history.text: Council approved Court Code. A list of S-M Ordinances on file at Great Lake Agency, BIA, includes Court Code.

annotations.annotation: Council approved Court Code October 4, 1988 by Resolution No. 1109. A list of S-M Ordinances on file at Great Lake Agency, BIA, includes Court Code. Resolution No. 1489-95 dated April 25, 1995, affirms Court Code of 1988.
